release.body:
## What's Changed
* Add profiles to ServiceDelegate, mark attributes as API by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container-attribute/pull/11
* Make attribute properties private by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container-attribute/pull/12


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container-attribute/compare/2.0.0-alpha.6...2.0.0-alpha.7

issue.title: Allow Profiles to be created using a CSV string
issue.body: Part of refactoring the `Cspray\AnnotatedContainer\Profiles` module includes removing the `CsvActiveProfilesParser`. We should provide similar functionality in a static constructor on the new `Profiles` value object.
